  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Vampire Survivor</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Auto Chess</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 rounds of battle. After the battle, enter the store to buy props to improve your abilities</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Five difficulties are waiting for you to challenge</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hundreds of items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The store can be upgraded. After upgrading, refresh to get more items and higher quality items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Some weapons can only be equipped in the middle grid, and some will occupy more than one item slot. There are backpacks to temporarily store items, multiple bonds, and richer strategies</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/e552ac0ebff8e3fc7271b6068b7b9f90.poster.avif?t=1700648991\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/e552ac0ebff8e3fc7271b6068b7b9f90.webm?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/e552ac0ebff8e3fc7271b6068b7b9f90.mp4?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple professions, each profession has at least six unique weapons</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/5b9369b3217dedd8f5d16aecd73ce882.poster.avif?t=1700648991\" width=640 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/5b9369b3217dedd8f5d16aecd73ce882.webm?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/5b9369b3217dedd8f5d16aecd73ce882.mp4?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple BOSS</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different experience in each game</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3D Low Poly style</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After the battle is over, you can shrink the circle. You can choose to continue spawning monsters or enter the store</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Added rolling and drinking operations</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/200265c23ebd1668795881abde1ab3b3.poster.avif?t=1700648991\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/200265c23ebd1668795881abde1ab3b3.webm?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/200265c23ebd1668795881abde1ab3b3.mp4?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/427ca4888850d6b2b0a1a00ff16bbf89.poster.avif?t=1700648991\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/427ca4888850d6b2b0a1a00ff16bbf89.webm?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446170/extras/427ca4888850d6b2b0a1a00ff16bbf89.mp4?t=1700648991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
